{
  "stem": "7832.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I just-- my body just became numb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mind was like, I didn't care when I died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because eventually, I was gonna die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only hoping to hang on long enough to die where the gas chambers wouldn't be around anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I didn't want to become ashes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so with the help of God, I guess, I endured.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the help like that nurse with other people around that, we weren't even aware that they were helping us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And like my friend Sabka with the support of trying to explain to me and make me strong and to maybe understand a little better why to live.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I guess all this put together and remembering what I lost and remembering that they will never be and maybe I will be lucky enough to do things for them, the things that they can't do anymore.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so with all of this put together, I think I had more luck than-- that sense.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as a 13-year-old, maybe it was more possible for me than for a 20-year-old or 30-year-old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The answer is not-- is not-- I don't have the-- the-- the right or the wrong or the-- or the answer to that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The fact is that I know that I-- sometimes, I wished I was dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes, I was walking the road where I knew they were gonna kill me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometimes I just wanted to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So just depends, you know, what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and terrible things happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My friend Sabka was taken away from-- from that barrack on the next zahlappell, and I was left again in the-- in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know where she went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know where they took her.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
